Height (m)

If ratio > 10, consider repair of aorta

Cholesterol mg/dL to mmol/L

1 mg/dL = 0.02586 mmol/L; 1 mmol/L = 38.7 mg/dL

Thus, 130 mg/dL = 3.45 mmol/L

Total cholesterol = LDL cholesterol + HDL cholesterol + 0.20 (Triglyceride level) HDL, high-density lipoprotein; LDL, low-density lipoprotein

